{"tid":1977123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼超越菲律賓成為東南亞最多人確診的國家","createTime":"2020-04-17T17:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T09:28:30.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"768f1ce987ac98ebdf19fda10c0c1fe45e23215f","tid":1977123,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1521232_1_20200417191800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1521232_1_20200417191800.jpg&h=0053cb25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼成為最多人確診的東南亞國家，工人在工廠製造口罩。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n印尼再多407人確診新型肺炎，累計5923人染病，超越菲律賓成為東南亞最多人感染的國家。死亡病例增加24宗，至今420人不治。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓新增218宗確診病例，再多25人死亡，累計近5900人染病，387人不治。警方說，有12萬人違反封城令，包括參與鬥雞及拳擊比賽，總統杜特爾特警告讓軍警介入，情況將會好像戒嚴一樣。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞單日新增69宗確診個案，數字是上月18日以來最少，累計超過5200人染病，死亡人數增至86人。泰國再多28宗確診及一宗死亡病例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521232-20200417.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521232-20200417.htm&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=0a12f2b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521232-20200417.htm&h=c3356afe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521232-20200417.htm</a>"},{"pid":"31616d969313af44a1159b3b4e697af27ffa5eaf","tid":1977123,"uid":189109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:24:40.000Z","msg":"Sinkeyore 好快追過啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba26e529277d108063be4cac540c25ebf3a6b33","tid":1977123,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:29:22.000Z","msg":"唔係話無錢做test 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d5360bf9a374ba63809463cb09fd953a4b3417","tid":1977123,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:35:08.000Z","msg":"印尼會唔會黎多次排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d7059566c0b2792ca88eeee91e484407c2afc9","tid":1977123,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:35:30.000Z","msg":"做口罩既人都唔識戴口罩<br />\n右手邊白白袍紅色恤衫個印仔<br />\n自己戴住個口罩但冇壓鐵絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會唔多人中招呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104161b0070a12cae8fa0ef386c4601de0118f01","tid":1977123,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21d7059566c0b2792ca88eeee91e484407c2afc9","tid":1977123,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:35:30.000Z","msg":"做口罩既人都唔識戴口罩<br />\n右手邊白白袍紅色恤衫個印仔<br />\n自己戴住個口罩但冇壓鐵絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會唔多人中招呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"全圖相信得最左嗰個印仔有稍微壓鐵片之外其他都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d7c098c9be9a9f529f8fd71e9b935454b9e50c","tid":1977123,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31616d969313af44a1159b3b4e697af27ffa5eaf","tid":1977123,"uid":189109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:24:40.000Z","msg":"Sinkeyore 好快追過啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"2日都唔洗，厲害了我的猴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡超越印尼成最多確診個案東南亞國家<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】新加坡再多數百人感染新型冠狀病毒，超越印尼成為最多確診個案的東南亞國家。<br />\n<br />\n截至中午，新加坡再增加596宗病例。累計六千五百多宗，新增病例的患者大部分，是住在宿舍的外勞，只有25人是新加坡公民或永久居民；南韓新增病例回落至個位數，昨日增加8宗，總理丁世均宣布，延長保持社交距離措施至5月5日；至於台灣就新增22宗確診個案，其中21宗的患者，是海軍敦睦艦隊成員。<br />\n<br />\n內地周六新增16宗病例，9宗屬於境外輸入，其餘7宗本地個案出現在黑龍江及廣東。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388230&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=7b6f1f6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388230&h=1905138c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388230</a>"}]}